{"tid":250673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對飲食業已經死心","createTime":"2017-05-20T09:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T17:10:15.000Z","uid":113664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b800c5a3908a806406fd90c1994cff0068cd673","tid":250673,"uid":113664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:17:24.000Z","msg":"我係一個返緊學既炒散<br />\n之前返個間大家嘻嘻哈哈過一日<br />\n得閒一齊聽下歌 傾下計<br />\n點煮一樣野先係最好食<br />\n個大佬又冇架子<br />\n因為人事變動大家都各散東西<br />\n其實呢啲同事真係好難搵到<br />\n後來轉左地方<br />\n先知做廚房原來係一個地獄<br />\n個地方已經定死左<br />\n仲要啲同事啲說話難撚聽到仆街<br />\n冇做錯野係要搵啲野入下你串尻你先過癮<br />\n其他人教我點做野<br />\n我一跟個同事點做個大佬即刻話尻我<br />\n你平時見撚到人地點做唔撚屌佢<br />\n係要屌尻我 真係好撚無癮 <br />\n淨係對撚住我咁撚緊<br />\n唔撚明咩心態"},{"pid":"8afe08e934328b5fb752edaf44a8030722b20c01","tid":250673,"uid":101262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:22:36.000Z","msg":"打個飛機<br />\n聽日繼續返工吧啦"},{"pid":"7d64374d1f18b55f9a5b0219e79439163953639a","tid":250673,"uid":7078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"去吉野家做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52592589e0bcbcf5e1b20c54946aad9188d82129","tid":250673,"uid":113664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打個飛機<br />\n聽日繼續返工吧啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好撚sad <br />\n我做咩都係錯"},{"pid":"c323f7c8472515c1c61c1ddf70cead8157a630e7","tid":250673,"uid":113664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:25:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去吉野家做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吉野家好做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e62c9fcbadaeabcc039edf5ec619f4624396a5f","tid":250673,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":